The accident reportedly took place close to Ngodwana. Motorists are advised to use the Schoemanskloof Road as an alternative to and from Nelspruit. TRAC sent a traffic update saying that the road is currently closed.  Reports are that the delay is caused by a chemical spill that needs to be cleaned up. • 20 to 30 minute delays have also been reported near eMalahleni between the Swartbos and Vosman off ramps, due to road works. 